metadata.name: Tingles
metadata.description:
Volume up!

Thinking of a way to recreate the tingling sensations you get from being lightly touched in moments of intimacy, this is what I came up with. Powerful, tiny bolts of electricity firing through your nerves.

All created by me, including the music :) Really hard self portrait to make! Made from 10 photos with a blue paper covered light swinging slowly on a string, with one end of the string in my hand to lower it!

The original higher bitrate 4k version will be sent to the collector.
metadata.Thankyou!: Send me a message on twitter so I can thank you properly!
